      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2812-2841",
      "markText": "党内如果没有矛盾和解决矛盾的思想斗争，党的生命也就停止了。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2812&rangeEnd=2841",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2812&rangeEnd=2841"
