      "range": "10288-10353",
      "markText": "矛盾的普遍性与特殊性，共性与个性的关系，是矛盾学说的精髓，懂得了它，就可以一通百通。古人所谓闻道，以今观之，就是闻这个矛盾之道”。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=10288&rangeEnd=10353",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=10288&rangeEnd=10353"
