      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "6468-6531",
      "markText": "但是光有对错误的政治路线与军事路线的批判，不可能彻底克服其影响。因为错误的政治路线与军事路线是以其深层的错误思想路线为基础的。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6468&rangeEnd=6531",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=6468&rangeEnd=6531"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_1_523-587",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "523-587",
      "markText": "日本东京大学教授近藤邦康公开宣称：“我很佩服《论持久战》。日本被中国打败是当然的，这样的以哲学为基础的宏远战略眼光，日本没有。”",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=523&rangeEnd=587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=523&rangeEnd=587"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_3_6158-6195",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6158-6195",
      "markText": "唯物辩证法认为外因是变化的条件。内因是变化的根据，外因通过内因而起作用。”",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6158&rangeEnd=6195",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6158&rangeEnd=6195"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_3_4206-4239",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4206-4239",
      "markText": "庸俗进化论的特点是以量变否定质变，以渐进否定飞跃，以改良否定革命。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4206&rangeEnd=4239",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4206&rangeEnd=4239"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_3_3761-3852",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3761-3852",
      "markText": "这就是说，不在联系上观察自然，而在孤立形态上观察它；不在其运动上观察自然，而在其静止上观察它；不把它当作根本变化的东西去观察，而把它当作固定不变的东西去观察；不观察其生，而观察其死。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3761&rangeEnd=3852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3761&rangeEnd=3852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_4_3905-3946",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3905-3946",
      "markText": "它要求我们对任何事物都要作矛盾分析，都要敢于揭露矛盾，善于分析矛盾，正确解决矛盾。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3905&rangeEnd=3946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3905&rangeEnd=3946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25010997_3_426-464",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "426-464",
      "markText": "主张物质是第一性、精神是第二性的，即主张物质规定精神的那种宇宙观是唯物论的。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25010997&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=426&rangeEnd=464",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/88832600717da3358889b2f?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=426&rangeEnd=464"
    },
    {
